-- сЃ╗сЃЈсЃЃсѓисЃЦтђцсЂїуЋ░сЂфсѓІсЂЊсЂесЂ»уб║УфЇсЂДсЂЇсЂЙсЂЎсЂїсђЂ
--   UPDATEсЃ╗УеѓТГБсЃ╗сЃЄсЃ╝сѓ┐СИЇТЋ┤тљѕсЂесЂ»ТќГт«џсЂДсЂЇсЂЙсЂЏсѓЊсђѓ
-- сЃ╗ућЪТѕљт»ЙУ▒АсѓФсЃЕсЃасђЂжђБухљжаєсђЂNULLтЄдуљєсЂфсЂЕсЂ»Тюфуб║УфЇсЂДсЂЎсђѓ
-- сЃ╗тЈѓуЁДт░ѓућеSQLсЂДсЂЎсђѓ
-- ============================================================

SELECT
    'TBAZ017M' AS table_name,

    COUNT(*) AS total_row_count,

    SUM(
        CASE
            WHEN csv_md5 IS NULL
              OR TRIM(CAST(csv_md5 AS STRING)) = ''
            THEN 1
            ELSE 0
        END
    ) AS csv_md5_blank_count,

    SUM(
        CASE
            WHEN kudu_md5 IS NULL
              OR TRIM(CAST(kudu_md5 AS STRING)) = ''
            THEN 1
            ELSE 0
        END
    ) AS kudu_md5_blank_count,

    SUM(
        CASE
            WHEN csv_md5 IS NOT NULL
             AND TRIM(CAST(csv_md5 AS STRING)) <> ''
             AND kudu_md5 IS NOT NULL
             AND TRIM(CAST(kudu_md5 AS STRING)) <> ''
            THEN 1
            ELSE 0
        END
    ) AS both_md5_present_count,

    SUM(
        CASE
            WHEN csv_md5 IS NOT NULL
             AND TRIM(CAST(csv_md5 AS STRING)) <> ''
             AND kudu_md5 IS NOT NULL
             AND TRIM(CAST(kudu_md5 AS STRING)) <> ''
             AND TRIM(CAST(csv_md5 AS STRING))
                 = TRIM(CAST(kudu_md5 AS STRING))
            THEN 1
            ELSE 0
        END
    ) AS same_md5_count,

    SUM(
        CASE
            WHEN csv_md5 IS NOT NULL
             AND TRIM(CAST(csv_md5 AS STRING)) <> ''
             AND kudu_md5 IS NOT NULL
             AND TRIM(CAST(kudu_md5 AS STRING)) <> ''
             AND TRIM(CAST(csv_md5 AS STRING))
                 <> TRIM(CAST(kudu_md5 AS STRING))
            THEN 1
            ELSE 0
        END
    ) AS different_md5_count,

    ROUND(
        SUM(
            CASE
                WHEN csv_md5 IS NOT NULL
                 AND TRIM(CAST(csv_md5 AS STRING)) <> ''
                 AND kudu_md5 IS NOT NULL
                 AND TRIM(CAST(kudu_md5 AS STRING)) <> ''
                 AND TRIM(CAST(csv_md5 AS STRING))
                     = TRIM(CAST(kudu_md5 AS STRING))
                THEN 1
                ELSE 0
            END
        ) * 100.0
        /
        NULLIF(
            SUM(
                CASE
                    WHEN csv_md5 IS NOT NULL
                     AND TRIM(CAST(csv_md5 AS STRING)) <> ''
                     AND kudu_md5 IS NOT NULL
                     AND TRIM(CAST(kudu_md5 AS STRING)) <> ''
                    THEN 1
                    ELSE 0
                END
            ),
            0
        ),
        4
    ) AS same_md5_rate_pct,

    FROM_UTC_TIMESTAMP(
        UTC_TIMESTAMP(),
        'Asia/Tokyo'
    ) AS executed_at_jst

FROM ai21rep_pr_kudu.tbaz017m

UNION ALL

